race.comment: LADY OF SAVOY (5) looks hard to beat. Ran on well to finish a close-up fifth second-up and has placed both tries when third up. Fitter and looks ready to win. ZOULAR (2) is going better than form suggests. Not far away when fifth off a wide gate at Mount Gambier last time and although drawn out again could push forward here and take catching. SUENAMI ROSE (6) was a close-up fourth at the provincials two back then fifth at Morphettville on the Parks track latest. Well placed here and worth another chance. SIX STARS (4) ran a much improved race last time over the border and a repeat would be good enough to feature in this. COMMANDER MEROO (3) has been thereabouts without winning but has the figures to go close.
